{"tid":1687174,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真香港人 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:58:41.000Z","uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46a333af41c7a529d81f0195cfc42929500659bb","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"睇完屠龍小隊既op 好有感觸<br />\n原文如下<br />\n勇武遺書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1686852\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1686852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽日就係大戰之時<br />\n好老實 我唔想再見到任何一位手足犧牲<br />\n但係如果唔勇武抗暴 <br />\n我地點會取得最後勝利<br />\n<br />\n「勇武係迫出黎」 真係講得好岩<br />\n<br />\n煲底除罩<br />\n仲可唔可以相遇番最初一齊出黎既前線手足<br />\n我好厭惡自己係女仔 又細粒 體能又唔好<br />\n剩係可以用對腳做抗爭 行足一日 哨足一日<br />\n為既就係 真正幫到前線既手足們<br />\n<br />\n我之所以會做哨 係想盡我最大能力保護好每一位手足<br />\n你地 聽日會出黎既 可唔可以應承我<br />\n不受傷 不流血 不被捕<br />\n雖然都知決定權唔係你地手上<br />\n真係好希望 前線手足 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n聽日 維園見啦各位 <br />\n如果打贏存活到<br />\n可唔可以開po一人一個擁抱<br />\n<br />\n利申：原文睇到阿止果句開頭已經喊左出黎"},{"pid":"bf04a3e17aa1abc4b1d804049f844180e1e87ff5","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e2ac47e56ab8fbd65b0112aeb23d7a9ecc84ade0","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f4a6dd30122d10c6c319ae059ea0b604be3eccc","tid":1687174,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6b57067102e287c8d3e972012a04e848117de49","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3ef5e99e40e88cc11ee56510a86781d8c9d51e7","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a511e6dc2cafb572afa3f7b8ae5176ec50645946","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fa71366c2082d0373cc08e18872cf2059ef0e98","tid":1687174,"uid":288767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"希望有人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf2e8146ec528f052b2bd498e55119648c24a5c","tid":1687174,"uid":311563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"我睇到啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}